---
---

<section id="servizi" class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="container-custom space-y-16">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold">
        I Nostri <span class="gradient-text">Servizi</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-dark-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Quattro linee di fatturato disegnate per portare i tuoi risultati da €0 a €1M+ annui
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Servizio 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark-900 to-dark-800 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary-500/20 hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-3">Piano di Lanci</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Esecuzione completa di lanci infobusiness. Il nostro modello "armatura di Iron Man" fornisce team integrato (copy, media buying, vendita) solo quando serve.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Workshop Funnel 5-7 giorni</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Team integrato on-demand</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Risultati verificati (MER 14.63x - 24.78x)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Servizio 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark-900 to-dark-800 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary-500/20 hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-3">Info Scaling</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Percorso 1:1 con Mario Olivelli. Strategia personalizzata di scaling per infoprenditori che vogliono crescere da €0 a €1M+ in modo sistematico.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Sessioni one-to-one con Mario</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Strategia di scaling personalizzata</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Accesso ai "tavoli riservati"</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Servizio 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark-900 to-dark-800 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary-500/20 hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 19H9a6 6 0 016-6v0a6 6 0 016 6v0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-3">Info Mastering</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Mastermind di gruppo per infoprenditori. Peer learning ad alto ticket con supervisione diretta di Mario Olivelli.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Peer mastermind group</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Accountability settimanale</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Accesso a framework proprietari</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Servizio 4 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark-900 to-dark-800 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary-500/20 hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-3">Codex10™</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Il sistema completo in 10 step per scalare da €10-15k/mese a €1M+ annui. From zero to hero.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>10 pilastri del business</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Video training completo</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary-500">✓</span>
            <span>Accesso anticipato</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
